Responsibility

Use of STL in operational, governance, infrastructure, AI, or safety-critical contexts is undertaken entirely at the user’s own responsibility.

STL provides structural collapse admissibility discipline and deterministic replay guarantees under declared scope.

It does not provide operational authority, certification, or safety guarantees.


